  ('diplomatic-1c87f27b-moex-00582', 'diplomatic-1c87f27b', 'diplomatic-1c87f27b-moex-110-e6f33b51', 'sub-diplomatic-1c87f27b-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者屬於非關稅壁壘的措施？', '["中央銀行的貨幣政策", "政府採購政策", "匯率政策", "財政政策"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:25:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ab8dabb335f2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f7c4ac93c413", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110150", "c": "101", "s": "1101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "國際經濟", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "diplomatic", "civil_category": "外交領事人員-土耳其文組"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('diplomatic-1c87f27b-moex-00583', 'diplomatic-1c87f27b', 'diplomatic-1c87f27b-moex-110-e6f33b51', 'sub-diplomatic-1c87f27b-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '根據產品生命週期（productlifecycle）模型，對比較利益的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["當產品的發展已成熟，比較利益將可能由原產品發明國轉移至其他國家", "對農產品或同質的工業產品而言，比較利益與這些產品所處的生命週期階段有關", "不論產品所處生命週期為何，原發明國將持續保有比較利益的地位", "比較利益與一國所擁有的技術勞動資源與研究發展產品的能力有關"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:25:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ab8dabb335f2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f7c4ac93c413", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110150", "c": "101", "s": "1101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "國際經濟", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "diplomatic", "civil_category": "外交領事人員-土耳其文組"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('diplomatic-1c87f27b-moex-00584', 'diplomatic-1c87f27b', 'diplomatic-1c87f27b-moex-110-e6f33b51', 'sub-diplomatic-1c87f27b-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '因加入區域貿易組織，使一國減少與非會員國之貿易，改偏向會員國進行貿易之現象稱為：', '["貿易轉移（tradediversion）", "貿易扭曲（tradedistortion）", "貿易排除（tradeexclusion）", "貿易創造（tradecreation）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:25:03+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "ab8dabb335f2", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f7c4ac93c413", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110150", "c": "101", "s": "1101", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "國際經濟", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "diplomatic", "civil_category": "外交領事人員-土耳其文組"}'::jsonb, NULL),
